ri si mai mult in depresie, te isterizezi si iti auto instalezi o stare de neliniste.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Stateam si ma gandeam azi de ce intra oamenii in depresie.Am gasit cateva raspunsuri care nu stiu daca sunt general valabile dar pentru unii cu siguranta.Oamenii intra in depresie pentru&nbsp;[&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7,28,5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/281"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=281"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/281\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":367,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/281\/revisions\/367"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=281"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=281"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=281"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}